{"id":160360,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/global-voices-斯里兰卡：自由贸易区抗争/","date":"2011-06-12T06:33:59Z","modified":"2011-06-12T06:33:59Z","title":"Global Voices | 斯里兰卡：自由贸易区抗争","content":"<p><p>本月初，斯里兰卡Katunayake自由贸易区劳工与警察爆发冲突，造成一名年轻工人丧命，另有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.jdslanka.org/2011/05/over-100-hurt-in-sri-lanka-workers.html\" href=\"http://www.jdslanka.org/2011/05/over-100-hurt-in-sri-lanka-workers.html\">逾200位警民受伤</a>，劳工是为反对政府所提出的私人退休金制度。</p>\n<p>该贸易区占全国出口量<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.ft.lk/2011/06/10/govt-will-consider-compensation-on-boi-recommendation/\" href=\"http://www.ft.lk/2011/06/10/govt-will-consider-compensation-on-boi-recommendation/\">约三成</a>，多数为服饰业，也名列全国外汇前三名；由于警民冲突，导致自由贸易区关闭，造成重大损失。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/vikalpasl/5785967080/in/set-72157626734568921\"><img title=\"ftz protest\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/ftz-protest.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" /></a></p>\n<p>6月1日，工会联盟号召民众赴首都火车站前，抗议警方攻击手无寸铁的自由贸易区劳工，照片来自Flickr用户Vikalpasl，依据创用CC BY-NC授权使用</p>\n</div>\n<p><em>Rasika Jayakody</em>在Groundviews<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/people-are-not-a-flock-of-sheep-the-murder-of-a-21-year-old-by-the-police/\" href=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/people-are-not-a-flock-of-sheep-the-murder-of-a-21-year-old-by-the-police/\">指出</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>除了一人丧命，警方暴力攻击自由贸易区劳工，导致逾200人受伤，在星期一晚上，Ragama和Negombo两间医院人满为患，这肯定是近年来一大严重事件；網絡上出现不少影片，证明警方面对手无寸铁的抗议民众时，行为既野蛮又无人性。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Groundviews网站于星期四<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/protests-in-katunayake-free-trade-zone-no-police-in-sight/\" href=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/protests-in-katunayake-free-trade-zone-no-police-in-sight/\">张贴</a>多段由<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/vikalpasl\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/vikalpasl\">Vikalpa</a>拍摄的影片，记录警察杀害21岁劳工Roshan Chanaka之后的情况，以下为其中一段：</p>\n</p>\n<p>此事发生后，斯里兰卡警察总监Mahinda Balasuirya<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.eelanatham.info/?p=771\" href=\"http://www.eelanatham.info/?p=771\">辞职</a>，两名引发冲突的员警遭到<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.groundreport.com/World/Two-Police-Officers-Who-Involved-In-Clash-With-Fre/2939347\" href=\"http://www.groundreport.com/World/Two-Police-Officers-Who-Involved-In-Clash-With-Fre/2939347\">逮捕</a>，总统亦下令调查。</p>\n<p>事件隔天，数百名佛教僧侣首度<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://blogs.geegain.com/post/14156/the-limits-of-the-mahinda-chintanaya-ftz-workers-and-buddhist-monks-rise-up-against-government\" href=\"http://blogs.geegain.com/post/14156/the-limits-of-the-mahinda-chintanaya-ftz-workers-and-buddhist-monks-rise-up-against-government\">出面</a>，在总统官邸外抗议杀戮。</p>\n<p><em>Serendipity</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://kalpanakaranna.blogspot.com/2011/06/who-is-behind-this-sinister-plot-to.html\" href=\"http://kalpanakaranna.blogspot.com/2011/06/who-is-behind-this-sinister-plot-to.html\">质疑</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>谁下令使用真枪实弹？谁下令准用铁棒？为何不动用经过训练的镇暴警察？为何不改用水柱？</p>\n<p>自由贸易区没有雇主参加抗争也令人意外，我只能揣测是因为政府暗示，“若反对政府，我们会让你的日子很难过”，利用恐惧让雇主噤声。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这场抗争对斯里兰卡有何意义？<em>Rasika Jayakody</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/people-are-not-a-flock-of-sheep-the-murder-of-a-21-year-old-by-the-police/\" href=\"http://groundviews.org/2011/06/03/people-are-not-a-flock-of-sheep-the-murder-of-a-21-year-old-by-the-police/\">说明</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这场抗争是自由贸易区劳工发动，为政府高层人士带来震撼教育，他们过去沉迷于权力与高位，但这场抗争让官员清楚明白，人们对于种种自负政治行为多么愤怒。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/rezwan/\" title=\"文章导读 Rezwan\">Rezwan</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/06/10/sri-lanka-protests-in-katunayake-free-trade-zone/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/06/12/9295/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%96%AF%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E5%8C%BA%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F12%2F9295%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F12%2F9295%2F&#038;desc=%E6%96%AF%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E5%8C%BA%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F12%2F9295%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F12%2F9295%2F&#038;text=%E6%96%AF%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E5%8C%BA%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F12%2F9295%2F&#038;title=%E6%96%AF%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E5%8C%BA%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.glob